a serves as president of prudential capital and investment services llc mr simmons joined the nasdaq omx group inc in february  and served as its chief executive officer from february  to may   he served as the unit president and chairman of the board at lions gate entertainment corp he served as president of the bond club of new york the he began his career in the securities industry in  when he  served as a financial advisor at hayden stone a predecessor firm of shearson lehman brothers inc he served as president of the private client group at shearson lehman brothers inc from  to  from may  to january  mr simmons served as president and chief executive officer of prudential securities incorporated and president of its subsidiary prudential sgroup inc since  he served as vice president in charge of data processing and communications division of hayden sponsible for retail sales and administration since  he served as senior executive vice president overseeing marketing and sales for shearsonamerican express since  he served in the us marine corps reserve from  to  he serves as the chairman of the national research exchange inc he has been a director of geneva acquisition corp since august  mr simmons has been an independent director of lions gate entertainment corp since june   he serves as a director of invivoscribe technologies inc and national academy foundation he serves as a trustee of groton school and woods hole oceanographic institution he served as chairman of securities industry and financial markets association he served as an independent nonexecutive director of raymond james financial inc from may   to february   and served as its lead director from  to february   mr simmons served as a director of the nasdaq omx group inc from september  to may   he served as a director of the partnership for new york city inc he served as a director of chicago board options exchange inc and nyc inc he serves as a trustee of the rippowam cisqua school in mt kisco new york he is a member of global advisory council at wta tour inc he was the chairman of the international tennis hall of fame he was a member of the nasd board of governors since  mr simmons graduated from harvard university with a ba in  and received his mba from the harvard business school in read full background corporate headquarters  broad streetnewark new jersey united statesphone fax  board members memberships trusteewoods hole oceanographic institutiontrusteegroton schooldirectornational academy foundationdirectorinvivoscribe technologies incpresentindependent directorlions gate entertainment corppresentdirectorgeneva acquisition corp education ba harvard universitymba harvard business school other affiliations raymond james financial inclions gate entertainment corpharvard universityprudential equity group llcnasdaq incharvard business schoolshearson lehman brothers incwoods hole oceanographic institutiongroton schoolnyc incbond club of new york thethe partnership for new york city incnational academy foundationwta tour incinvivoscribe technologies incthe national research exchange incgeneva acquisition corpcboe holdings inc annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data available total compensation there is no total compensation data available request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup competitor compensationthere is no competitor compensation data available sponsored financial commentaries sponsored links browse companies a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z              request profile update only a company representative may request an update for the company pro